Gaylord Lloyd https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaylord_Lloyd 0 Gaylord Lloyd (March 20, 1888 - September 1, 1943) was an actor and assistant director, known for Dodge Your Debts (1921), Trolley Troubles (1921) and Why Worry? (1923). He was the older brother of actor Harold Lloyd. He was married to Barbara Starr. He was born in Burchard, Nebraska, and died in Beverly Hills, Los Angeles, California.
